data.description:
Available June 1st. This nice 3 bed 2 bath town house includes all kitchen appliances, walk in closets, a large 2 car attached garage and a spacious laundry room. It has 1400 sq feet of finished space and a 750 sq ft unfinished basement for oodles of storage or an area for the kids to during inclement weather. HOA does all the yard work and community enjoys walking trails and picnic areas. HOA fees included in rent. It's walking distance from the elementary school and the neighborhood has lots of children. Pets allowed with $400 pet deposit and $25 a month additional pet fee. For an appointment to see this lovely home, please call Brent at Parker Brown 801-897-1844

1 or more years
No smokers
Tenant pays electricity, gas, internet, and cable if desired
